page_desc_en:
The retina contains 2 types of photoreceptors;
rod cells - sensitive to different intensities of light.
cone cells - sensitive to the color of light in bright conditions

page_desc_ms:
Retina mengandungi 2 jenis fotoreseptor;
sel rod - sensitif terhadap keamatan cahaya yang berbeza.
sel kon - sensitif terhadap warna cahaya dalam keadaan terang
